Who We Are

Two Decades
Below the Surface

// HDD Operation in Progress
// Pipe Entry Point

Founded in 2003, McCowien Construction LLC has built a reputation for quality workmanship, dependable scheduling, and strict safety standards. Our team handles the toughest underground environments — urban, rocky, waterlogged, or high-volume infrastructure.

We get the job done right the first time. Advanced drilling and excavation methods mean minimal surface disruption — roads stay open, property stays intact, and projects stay on schedule.

What We Do

Underground
Construction Services

Our equipment and trained crews work efficiently in challenging soil, rock, and urban environments — any depth, any condition.

01
🔩
Horizontal Directional Drilling

Precision HDD beneath roads, waterways, and structures with zero surface disruption. Our flagship capability.

02
🪨
Rock Drilling

Specialized equipment and techniques for drilling through hard rock formations in any terrain or depth.

03
💧
Hydro Excavation

Safe, precise excavation using pressurized water — ideal for exposing buried utilities without damage.

04
⚡
Electric Conduit Installation

Underground electrical conduit systems for utility providers and commercial infrastructure projects.

05
🌐
Fiber Optic Cable

High-speed fiber optic installation for telecommunications networks — minimal disruption, maximum efficiency.

06
🔥
Gas Line Installation

Certified gas line installation and replacement for residential, commercial, and municipal utility systems.

07
🚿
Water Line Installation

Underground water main and service line installation for municipalities and private clients.

08
🏗️
Septic & Sewer Lines

Complete septic system and sewer line installation, replacement, and rehabilitation services.

09
🌧️
Storm Drain Installation

Storm drainage system design and installation for municipalities, roads, and commercial sites.
